nodes.text: The Joben-Dusat Racing Team was a landspeeder racing team founded by Thall Joben and Jord Dusat. Working from their speeder shop on the planet Ingo, Joben and Dusat built the White Witch, a heavily modified Mobquet C/L-82 which Joben piloted to victory in the Boonta Speeder Race in 15 BBY.
